{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/4026", "repo": "rails", "body": "@drogus\r\n\r\nConsiders your proposal, I think the easiest way to fix that next.\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ vim lib/active_record/persistence.rb\r\n208     def update_attributes(attributes, options = {})\r\n209       # The following transaction covers any possible database side-effects of the\r\n210       # attributes assignment. For example, setting the IDs of a child collection.\r\n211       with_transaction_returning_status do\r\n212         self.assign_attributes(attributes, options)\r\n213         save(options) # \u2605 options argument is passed \r\n214       end\r\n215     end\r\n```\r\n\r\nWhat do you think?", "_id": {"$oid": "523f4028bd354364b9016352"}, "issue_id": 4026, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/3212740", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/4026#issuecomment-3212740", "updated_at": "2011-12-20T02:34:23Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj", "login": "kennyj", "gravatar_id": "1f0b221851379759360d7130dabdfa53", "html_url": "https://github.com/kennyj", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/1f0b221851379759360d7130dabdfa53?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F54ecc28e9508fcf28363014b0d1b4eb8.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 13426, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2011-12-20T01:20:38Z", "id": 321